float ln (vec3 p, vec3 a, vec3 b) {return length(p-a-(b-a)*min(dot(p-a,b-a),0.)/dot(b-a,b-a));}
void mainImage( out vec4 Q, in vec2 U )
{
    float 
        n = C(U+vec2(0,1)).x,
        e = C(U+vec2(1,0)).x,
        s = C(U-vec2(0,1)).x,
        w = C(U-vec2(1,0)).x;
    vec4 a = A(U);
    vec4 c = C(U);
    Q = vec4(0);
    Q = .6*atan(20.*c.z)*vec4(1,.12,0,1);
    Q += .3*atan(7.*c.z)*vec4(1,.1,0,1);
    Q -= atan(c.z)*vec4(1.,.1,-.1,1);
    Q += .3*abs(sin(.5*c.x*(1.+vec4(4,3,2,1))));
    Q += .2*c.y*vec4(0.1,0.4,0.9,1);
    Q = atan(Q);
    vec3 no = normalize(vec3(e-w,n-s,.3+.2*Q.w));
    float light = ln(vec3(1,1,2),vec3(U/R.y,0),vec3(U/R.y,0)+reflect(normalize(vec3((U-0.5*R)/R.y,1)),no));
    Q *= .8*exp(-.5*vec4(1,2,3,4)*light)+.8*exp(-.06*vec4(1,2,3,4)*light);
	Q = atan(3.*Q)*.666;

    U = 0.5*R-abs(U-0.5*R);
    Q += (0.5-0.5*cos(6.*a.z*(1.+.5*vec4(1,2,3,4))))*smoothstep(1.,-1.,min(U.x,U.y)-3.);


}

// Calculate forces and pressure
void mainImage( out vec4 Q, in vec2 U )
{
    Q = A(U);
    vec4 
        n = A(U+vec2(0,1)),
        e = A(U+vec2(1,0)),
        s = A(U-vec2(0,1)),
        w = A(U-vec2(1,0));
    Q.xy -= 
        // pressure force
        0.25*vec2(e.z-w.z,n.z-s.z)+
        // magnus force
        0.25*Q.w*vec2(n.w-s.w,e.w-w.w);
    // divergence
    Q.z  = 0.25*(s.y-n.y+w.x-e.x+n.z+e.z+s.z+w.z);
    // curl
    Q.w = 0.25*(s.x-n.x+w.y-e.y);
    vec4 c = C(U);
    Q.yz += vec2(0.01,.007)*c.z;
    Q.y -= 0.001*c.x;
    Q.xy *= .997;
    //Boundary conditions
    //vec2 JET = vec2(.5+.25*sin(float(iFrame)/500.),0.1)*R;
    //if (iMouse.z>0.) JET = iMouse.xy;
    //Q.xy = mix(Q.xy,vec2(0,.7),0.3*smoothstep(1.,-1.,length(U-JET)-6.));
    if (iFrame<1) Q = vec4(0);
    if (U.x<2.||U.y<2.||R.x-U.x<2.||R.y-U.y<2.)Q.xyw*=0.;
}

// Advect along velocity and curl feild
void mainImage( out vec4 Q, in vec2 U )
{
    for (float i = 0.; i< N;i++) {
        Q = A(U);
        float co = cos(Q.w/N), si = sin(Q.w/N);
        U -= Q.xy*mat2(co,-si,si,co)/N;
    }
    Q = A(U);
}

// Advect along velocity and curl feild
void mainImage( out vec4 Q, in vec2 U )
{
    for (float i = 0.; i< N;i++) {
        Q = A(U);
        float co = cos(Q.w/N), si = sin(Q.w/N);
        U -= Q.xy*mat2(co,-si,si,co)/N;
    }
    Q = C(U);
}

// draw color and acount for divergence
void mainImage( out vec4 Q, in vec2 U )
{
    Q = C(U);
    // neighborhood
    vec4 
        n = A(U+vec2(0,1)),
        e = A(U+vec2(1,0)),
        s = A(U-vec2(0,1)),
        w = A(U-vec2(1,0)),
    	nc = C(U+vec2(0,1)),
        ec = C(U+vec2(1,0)),
        sc = C(U-vec2(0,1)),
        wc = C(U-vec2(1,0));
    // divergence 
    Q += 0.25*(s.y*sc-n.y*nc+w.x*wc-e.x*ec);

    // x : fuel y : oxygen z flame

    Q = mix(Q,0.25*(nc+ec+sc+wc),vec4(.0,1.-Q.x,.6,0));

    float x = .25*Q.x*Q.y*Q.z;

    Q.z = Q.z*.84-1e-4 + 45.*x;
    Q.y += 0.004*(1.-Q.y)*Q.y-1e-3*Q.x-x;
    Q.x -= x;
    Q = max(Q,0.);
    if (iMouse.z>0.&&length(U-iMouse.xy)<3.)Q.yz = vec2(.01,1);
    // boundary conditions
    if(iFrame < 1) Q = mix(vec4(0,1,0,0),vec4(1,0,0,0),smoothstep(1.,-1.,min(length(U-0.5*R)-20.,U.y-100.)));
    if (U.x<2.||U.y<2.||R.x-U.x<2.||R.y-U.y<2.) Q=vec4(0,0,0,0);
	if (R.y-U.y<4.) Q.y = 1.;
}
